io.github.msdk.datamodel

Interface ActivationInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleActivationInfo

    @Immutable
public interface ActivationInfo
    Represents the fragmentation information of MS/MS experiments. For convenience, this interface is immutable, so it can be passed by reference and safely used by multiple threads.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Double getActivationEnergy()
      Returns the activation energy applied for this MS/MS scan.
      ActivationType getActivationType()
      Returns the type of the fragmentation (MS/MS) experiment.

    • Method Detail

      • getActivationType

        @Nonnull
ActivationType getActivationType()
        Returns the type of the fragmentation (MS/MS) experiment. If unknown, FragmentationType.UNKNOWN is returned.
        Returns:
        Fragmentation type

      • getActivationEnergy

        @Nullable
Double getActivationEnergy()
        Returns the activation energy applied for this MS/MS scan. This value has no dimension and its meaning depends on instrument. Null is returned if unknown.
        Returns:
        MS/MS activation energy, or null.
